Daemos received a transmission via the Hellgate. The message he had awaited 
since his first day on the planet.

Daemos:
Thank you, Belthassan, Melchana and Gesper. For the moment, I am about to 
enter a gladiator league. I am also about to conclude an agreement with 
Zardus the leader of the faction called the Alliance. They could assist us, 
for now. I will recommend you to Zardus.

(to Zardus):
I am on the move. (he started over to where Zardus was) But I must remind 
you that I will take part to the IGL and that I shall soon depart. If any of 
your troops need a ride aboard the Hellgate, it's on me. If you would like 
other troops to assist you, may I suggest that you contact Commander 
Belthassan in Australia? He is an old comrade, and he has just established a 
base there...
